data.description: Seize the opportunity to assume a low mortgage interest rate of 2.8% with this VA Assumable Mortgage Loan! Enjoy the luxury of lakeside living and access to horse stables maintained exclusively for you and your neighbors. A rare blend of lakes and equestrian amenities, this is a world where dreams do become reality!  Immerse yourself in the charm of this GOLF CART FRIENDLY community, where you can explore the tranquility and amenities of Lake Padgett Estates or simply relish breathtaking sunsets right from the comfort of your front window.  With 3 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms, this split floor plan blends form and function, promising privacy, comfort, and convenience for every member of the household. Escape to the master bedroom's bonus room, a haven for relaxation. Whether you're crafting a home office, a yoga studio, or simply a tranquil reading nook, this space is your canvas to paint with creativity.  Celebrate life's special moments with your loved ones in your expansive fenced in backyard complete with a double gate. Park your boat with ease after a leisurely cruise around Lake Padgett, or effortlessly accommodate your RV, fueling your sense of adventure. Call today to arrange your private showing.  Lake Padgett Estates isn't just a community, it's a lifestyle.  Seller pays for title and selects Cloud Title.
